column2: SELECT      p.ra,p.dec,p.z,       dbo.fPhotoTypeN(sp.type) as photo_type,      str(p.modelMag_u,#,#) as u,str(p.modelMagErr_u,#,#) as err_u, str(p.extinction_u,#,#) as ux,      str(p.modelMag_g,#,#) as g,str(p.modelMagErr_g,#,#) as err_g, str(p.extinction_g,#,#) as gx,      str(p.modelMag_r,#,#) as r,str(p.modelMagErr_r,#,#) as err_r, str(p.extinction_r,#,#) as rx,      str(p.modelMag_i,#,#) as i,str(p.modelMagErr_i,#,#) as err_i, str(p.extinction_i,#,#) as ix,      str(p.modelMag_z,#,#) as z,str(p.modelMagErr_z,#,#) as err_z, str(p.extinction_z,#,#) as zx, pz.absMagR,   sp.plate, sp.mjd, sp.fiberid, str(sp.z,#,#) as spec_z, str(pz.z,#,#) as phot_z         FROM PhotoObjAll into MyDB.tmpcmass   LEFT OUTER JOIN PhotoObjAll p on n.objID = p.objID   LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON sp.objID =p.objID   LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID =p.objID             WHERE (sp.z >= # and sp.z <= #) OR (pz.z >= # and pz.z <=#)
